    <title class="- topic/title "><ph class="- topic/ph topic/title-wrapper ">Zotero for MS Office Word插件</ph></title>
    <shortdesc class="- topic/shortdesc ">Zotero for MS Office Word插件允许用户在Microsoft Word文档中直接插入和管理文献引用，以及创建参考文献表。</shortdesc>
    <conbody class="- topic/body  concept/conbody ">
        <p class="- topic/p ">一般情况下，Zotero 安装时会安装 Zotero Word 插件，其会在 Microsoft Word 里添加一个 Zotero
                选项卡，提供了添加/编辑引注、添加/编辑参考文献表、添加笔记、文档首选项、刷新和取消链接引注等功能。如下图所示：<image class="- topic/image " href="file:/C:/Users/35461/Desktop/7.%20在word中使用Zotero引用文献/7-image/Zotero%20Word%20插件选项卡.png" id="unique_1_Connect_42_image_f5j_db3_mdc" nd:nd-id="image_f5j_db3_mdc" placement="break" width="300"/></p>
    </conbody>
</concept><task break-before="true" is-chapter="true" class="- topic/topic task/task " id="unique_2" topicrefclass="- map/topicref " nd:nd-id="insert-references" oid="insert-references" specializations="@props/deliveryTarget">
    <title class="- topic/title "><ph class="- topic/ph topic/title-wrapper ">插入参考文献</ph></title>
    <shortdesc class="- topic/shortdesc ">介绍如何在Word中通过Zotero插入参考文献。</shortdesc>
    <taskbody class="- topic/body task/taskbody ">
        <context class="- topic/section task/context ">
            <p class="- topic/p ">在Word中通过Zotero插入参考文献的步骤如下：</p>
        </context>
        <steps class="- topic/ol task/steps ">
            <step class="- topic/li task/step ">
                <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">打开Zotero和Word，同时加载Word文档。</cmd>
            </step>
            <step class="- topic/li task/step ">
                <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">在Word中将光标放置在需要插入引用的位置。</cmd>
            </step>
            <step class="- topic/li task/step ">
                <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">点击<uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Add/Edit Citation</uicontrol>按钮。</cmd>
            </step>
            <step class="- topic/li task/step ">
                <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">在一个未添加过引文的文档中，按下按钮将先弹出一个「文档首选项」窗口以选择一个 CSL 样式，之后再点<uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Add/Edit
                        Citation</uicontrol>将直接显示「引注对话框」，这个对话框可以从 Zotero
                        库中选择条目，并创建引注。在对话框中键入标题的一部分、一个或多个作者的姓氏和/或年份。匹配项将立即显示在对话框下方。如下图所示：<image class="- topic/image " href="file:/C:/Users/35461/Desktop/7.%20在word中使用Zotero引用文献/7-image/引用文献.png" id="unique_2_Connect_42_image_awr_sr3_mdc" nd:nd-id="image_awr_sr3_mdc" placement="break" width="300"/></cmd>
            </step>
            <step class="- topic/li task/step ">
                <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">单击某条目选择这个条目，或用键盘「↑↓」+「Enter」键来选择条目。选中的条目以气泡形状显示在对话框中。完成选择后，再次按「Enter/Return」键以插入引注并关闭引注对话框。如下图所示：<image class="- topic/image " href="file:/C:/Users/35461/Desktop/7.%20在word中使用Zotero引用文献/7-image/引文对话框png.png" id="unique_2_Connect_42_image_ezb_ms3_mdc" nd:nd-id="image_ezb_ms3_mdc" placement="break" width="400"/></cmd>
            </step>
        </steps>
    </taskbody>
</task><task break-before="true" is-chapter="true" class="- topic/topic task/task " id="unique_3" topicrefclass="- map/topicref " nd:nd-id="edit-delete-citations" oid="edit-delete-citations" specializations="@props/deliveryTarget">
    <title class="- topic/title "><ph class="- topic/ph topic/title-wrapper ">编辑或删除引注</ph></title>
    <shortdesc class="- topic/shortdesc ">在Word文档中编辑或删除已插入的引注。</shortdesc>
    <taskbody class="- topic/body task/taskbody ">
        <context class="- topic/section task/context ">
            <p class="- topic/p ">对已插入的引注进行编辑或删除，可采取以下步骤：</p>
        </context>
        <steps class="- topic/ol task/steps ">
            <step class="- topic/li task/step ">
                <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">编辑引注：</cmd>
                <info class="- topic/itemgroup task/info ">
                    <p class="- topic/p ">在已插入的引注中增加/删除条目，或者修改引注的信息，可以将光标定位在引注内（此时引注区域会出现灰色阴影），然后再单击<uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Add/Edit
                            Citation</uicontrol>按钮开始编辑引注。如下图所示：<image class="- topic/image " href="file:/C:/Users/35461/Desktop/7.%20在word中使用Zotero引用文献/7-image/编辑引注.jpg" id="unique_3_Connect_42_image_jxm_153_mdc" nd:nd-id="image_jxm_153_mdc" placement="break" width="300"/></p>
                </info>
            </step>
            <step class="- topic/li task/step ">
                <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">删除引注：</cmd>
                <info class="- topic/itemgroup task/info ">
                    <p class="- topic/p ">选中引注并按<uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Delete</uicontrol>键或右键选择<uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">删除</uicontrol>。</p>
                </info>
            </step>
        </steps>
    </taskbody>
</task><task break-before="true" is-chapter="true" class="- topic/topic task/task " id="unique_4" topicrefclass="- map/topicref " nd:nd-id="create-update-bibliography" oid="create-update-bibliography" specializations="@props/deliveryTarget">
    <title class="- topic/title "><ph class="- topic/ph topic/title-wrapper ">创建和更新参考文献表</ph></title>
    <shortdesc class="- topic/shortdesc ">在Word文档中创建和更新参考文献表。</shortdesc>
    <taskbody class="- topic/body task/taskbody ">
        <context class="- topic/section task/context ">
            <p class="- topic/p ">使用Zotero插件可以在Word中创建和更新参考文献表，步骤如下：</p>
        </context>
        <steps class="- topic/ol task/steps ">
            <step class="- topic/li task/step ">
                <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">创建参考文献表：</cmd>
                <info class="- topic/itemgroup task/info ">
                    <p class="- topic/p ">点击<uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Add/Edit
                            Bibliography</uicontrol>按钮，在文档中适当的位置插入参考文献表。如下图所示：<image class="- topic/image " href="file:/C:/Users/35461/Desktop/7.%20在word中使用Zotero引用文献/7-image/创建参考文献表.png" id="unique_4_Connect_42_image_usx_3v3_mdc" nd:nd-id="image_usx_3v3_mdc" placement="break" width="300"/></p>
                </info>
            </step>
            <step class="- topic/li task/step ">
                <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">更新参考文献表：</cmd>
                <info class="- topic/itemgroup task/info ">
                    <p class="- topic/p ">对文档中的引注进行更改后，点击<uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">刷新</uicontrol>按钮更新参考文献表。如下图所示：<image class="- topic/image " href="file:/C:/Users/35461/Desktop/7.%20在word中使用Zotero引用文献/7-image/更新参考文献表.png" id="unique_4_Connect_42_image_d3y_jv3_mdc" nd:nd-id="image_d3y_jv3_mdc" placement="break" width="300"/></p>
                </info>
            </step>
        </steps>
    </taskbody>
</task><task break-before="true" is-chapter="true" class="- topic/topic task/task " id="unique_5" topicrefclass="- map/topicref " nd:nd-id="switch-citations-style" oid="switch-citations-style" specializations="@props/deliveryTarget">
    <title class="- topic/title "><ph class="- topic/ph topic/title-wrapper ">切换引用样式</ph></title>
    <shortdesc class="- topic/shortdesc ">介绍如何在Word文档中切换不同的引用样式。</shortdesc>
    <taskbody class="- topic/body task/taskbody ">
        <context class="- topic/section task/context ">
            <p class="- topic/p ">使用Zotero插件在Word文档中切换引用样式的步骤如下：</p>
        </context>
        <steps class="- topic/ol task/steps ">
            <step class="- topic/li task/step ">
                <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">点击<uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Document Preferences</uicontrol>按钮。</cmd>
            </step>
            <step class="- topic/li task/step ">
                <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">在弹出的窗口中，选择新的CSL样式并点击<uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">OK</uicontrol>。如下图所示：<image class="- topic/image " href="file:/C:/Users/35461/Desktop/7.%20在word中使用Zotero引用文献/7-image/切换引用样式.png" id="unique_5_Connect_42_image_og3_dw3_mdc" nd:nd-id="image_og3_dw3_mdc" placement="break" width="300"/></cmd>
            </step>
        </steps>
    </taskbody>
</task><task break-before="true" is-chapter="true" class="- topic/topic task/task " id="unique_6" topicrefclass="- map/topicref " nd:nd-id="troubleshooting-zotero-word" oid="troubleshooting-zotero-word" specializations="@props/deliveryTarget">
    <title class="- topic/title "><ph class="- topic/ph topic/title-wrapper ">故障排除</ph></title>
    <shortdesc class="- topic/shortdesc ">解决在使用Zotero Word插件时遇到的常见问题。</shortdesc>
    <taskbody class="- topic/body task/taskbody ">
        <context class="- topic/section task/context ">
            <p class="- topic/p ">如果遇到Zotero插件未显示、引注未正确更新等问题，请按照以下步骤操作：</p>
        </context>
        <steps class="- topic/ol task/steps ">
            <step class="- topic/li task/step ">
                <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">检查插件安装。</cmd>
                <info class="- topic/itemgroup task/info ">
                    <p class="- topic/p ">确保Zotero插件已正确安装，且Word插件已启用。</p>
                </info>
            </step>
            <step class="- topic/li task/step ">
                <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">检查网络连接。</cmd>
                <info class="- topic/itemgroup task/info ">
                    <p class="- topic/p ">确保网络连接正常，以便Zotero可以同步库中的更改。</p>
                </info>
            </step>
            <step class="- topic/li task/step ">
                <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">重启Word和Zotero。</cmd>
                <info class="- topic/itemgroup task/info ">
                    <p class="- topic/p ">尝试重启Word和Zotero，重新建立连接。</p>
                </info>
            </step>
            <step class="- topic/li task/step ">
                <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">寻求帮助。</cmd>
                <info class="- topic/itemgroup task/info ">
                    <p class="- topic/p ">访问Zotero官方论坛或中文社区寻求帮助。</p>
                </info>
            </step>
        </steps>
    </taskbody>
</task></map>